caravan of courage : an ewok adventure ( originally broadcast as the ewok adventure ) is a 1984 american television film based in the star wars universe . it is the first of two spin-off films featuring the ewoks from return of the jedi . the film , which is set on the moon of endor some time after the ewoks animated series but before the events of return of the jedi , focuses on the struggles of a brother and sister trying to locate their parents who have been kidnapped by a monster known as the gorax .